Start!

328
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:35,720
Commander Zhang,

329
00:17:35,720 --> 00:17:36,440
from here on,

330
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:38,200
I really don't dare beat you anymore.

331
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:39,400
To be honest with you,

332
00:17:39,590 --> 00:17:40,480
Mr. Yuan is having bad luck.

333
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:42,610
I don't want to cause him more trouble.

334
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,660
The show's about to start!

