355
00:20:50,310 --> 00:20:52,680
Great! Great!

356
00:20:55,590 --> 00:20:58,190
Zhang is indeed
from an artillery background.

357
00:20:58,880 --> 00:21:00,140
He took the wrong road,

358
00:21:00,650 --> 00:21:02,580
but his artillery skills are good.

359
00:21:04,290 --> 00:21:05,820
The Northern Army is upset.

360
00:21:06,240 --> 00:21:09,100
Losing two rounds like that
seems a bit suspicious.

