00:21:09,750 --> 00:21:10,790
Upset about what?

362
00:21:11,740 --> 00:21:14,110
When two flowers blossom,
each has its own charm.

363
00:21:14,110 --> 00:21:14,840
If you ask me,

364
00:21:15,590 --> 00:21:18,250
they both
have their strengths and weaknesses.

365
00:21:19,240 --> 00:21:20,840
Northern Army, third round,

366
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:22,240
get ready!

367
00:21:29,720 --> 00:21:30,440
Fire!

368
00:21:44,110 --> 00:21:45,640
They're not firing cannons

369
00:21:45,910 --> 00:21:47,570
